Package: DPmixGPD
Type: Package
Title: Dirichlet Process Mixtures with Generalized Pareto Tail
Version: 0.0.8
Author: Arnab Aich [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Arnab Aich <arnab.aich99@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Arnab", "Aich", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "arnab.aich99@gmail.com")
Description: Experimental framework for Dirichlet process mixture regression and unconditional models
    with flexible kernels (gamma, lognormal, normal, Laplace, inverse Gaussian, Amoroso)
    and optional generalized Pareto (GPD) tail extension.
